# Cargo build directory — ~440 MB of compiled deps + intermediate
# artifacts. Reproduced by `cargo build --release` from Cargo.toml +
# Cargo.lock; never committed.
/target/

# Built native addons. The `index.cjs` loader resolves per-platform
# `.node` files (linux-x64-gnu, linux-x64-musl, …) at runtime; they
# are produced by the build pipeline (host: `cargo build --release`
# + rename; Alpine: Docker cross-build). Committing host-built
# binaries would mix platform artifacts with source.
*.node
